description:
This course will help to build solid foundation for trading, confidence and managing portfolio.You will be able to understand International Financial Markets structure and behavior, how to interpret, analyse and trade them.

I'll be conducting Live financial market analysis and will share with you the trade setups and how i will approach them. This will give you hands-on-practice confidence and also the skills that require to be a Technical Trader.
title: Weekly Forex Analysis by Baraq FX
